::SkarBlaise::
    He takes the shot in the chest leaving a shredded area and is knocked 
back and lands on is back again.  He shakes his head and sits up saying "Good 
stock."  He stands and looks at Fury and says "Good battle."  He takes a step 
forward ignoring the pain in his chest.  He raises his guns and fires a pair 
of missiles and four high power blasts from his gun.  As his shots leave his 
weapons he says "Good bye."
